you need to write your solution in the form of Function(s) only.
Driver Code to call/invoke your function is mentioned above.*/

int transitionPoint(int arr[],int n)
{
// Your code goes here
int transPoint = 0;
for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
    if(arr[i]==1){
    transPoint = i;
    break;
    }
}
return transPoint;
}
